---
title: Pan-Fried Garlic Butter Chicken Breast with Chips and Tomato Salad
description: This  Pan-Fried Garlic Butter Chicken Breast is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R01_W26_UK_F14614-6_main_swap_low-9fc0962c.jpg
